NAME
CFG_DIR - defines RPG configuration directory pathname

DESCRIPTION
The CFG_DIR environment variable defines the RPG configuration directory
pathname.

In the fielded software, this environment variable is set to "$HOME/cfg".

In the baselined software, this environment variable is set in one or more
user login environment files (e.g., .profile, .cshrc).

A developer or tester may set CFG_DIR to a non-baseline directory in order
to reference non-baseline configuration files.  This approach is preferred
to changing individual configuration filenames within the CFG_DIR
directory.

